Description:
    Generates a complete component scaffold for the UntitledUi design system.

    This generator creates:
    - app/components/ui/{name}/component.rb       — Ruby class extending Ui::Base
    - app/components/ui/{name}/component.html.erb — ERB template with root div
    - spec/components/ui/{name}_component_spec.rb — RSpec tests
    - app/views/untitled_ui/design_system/components/examples/_{name}.html.erb — Design system preview
    - Registers the component in the COMPONENTS array of components_controller.rb

    With --stimulus:
    - app/javascript/untitled_ui/{name}_controller.js — Stimulus controller
    - Registers the controller in app/javascript/untitled_ui/index.js

Usage:
    rails generate untitled_ui:scaffold NAME [options]

Arguments:
    NAME    The component name in snake_case (e.g. my_component, card_header)

Options:
    --stimulus
        Generate a Stimulus controller alongside the component.

    --slots=SLOT[,SLOT,...]
        Add renders_one slots to the component.
        Example: --slots=header,footer,actions

    --props=PROP_DEF[,PROP_DEF,...]
        Add props to the component's initializer.
        Each PROP_DEF can be:
          name              — string prop (defaults to nil)
          name:string       — explicit string prop
          name:boolean      — boolean prop (defaults to false)
          name:select:a:b:c — symbol prop restricted to given values (defaults to first value)
        Example: --props=size:select:sm:md:lg,disabled:boolean,label:string

Examples:
    # Basic scaffold
    rails generate untitled_ui:scaffold my_component

    # With a Stimulus controller
    rails generate untitled_ui:scaffold my_component --stimulus

    # With slots
    rails generate untitled_ui:scaffold card --slots=header,body,footer

    # With typed props
    rails generate untitled_ui:scaffold badge --props=size:select:sm:md:lg,color:select:gray:brand:error,dismissible:boolean

    # Full-featured example
    rails generate untitled_ui:scaffold notification \
      --stimulus \
      --slots=icon,actions \
      --props=variant:select:info:success:warning:error,dismissible:boolean,title:string
